content.name: DeadAir Ware
content.description:
DeadAir Ware
Scales production cycles to 10 minutes - Increases critical ship ware production amounts - Increases workforce effect to 50% and growthrate - Adjusts faction relation discounts to prevent unsellable goods - Lowers station module build time - Workforce now requires more food
Save game compatible.
Patch notes available on: https://github.com/DeadAirRT
Best place to contact me: https://forum.egosoft.com/viewtopic.php?f=181&t=415937
content.author: DeadAir
